CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 13, 1958, pg. A14 reads: "Guild Check - Mrs. Ann C. Waters, president of the Urban League Guild, presents a check to Richard Evarts, member of the Pittsburgh Urban League board of directors, at the Christmas luncheon held at the Press Club. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Men and women seated around banquet tables, including Richard Evarts, seated at back table on right, in Press Club for Urban League Guild Christmas luncheon
